oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Minutes of the Annual Business Luncheon. The meeting was called to order by AABP President, Dr. Calvin Booker, at 12:10 p.m. Dr. Booker presented the minutes of the St. Louis business meeting. On motion with a second, the minutes of the 2019 Annual Business Meeting were approved.
